OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FDeputy Rob Ward's new legislation now
OL,8,Fmeans that anyone hoping to win a seat
OL,9,Fwill be asked to declare links to
OL,10,Fpolitical groups, how those groups are
OL,11,Forganised, and where their funding
OL,12,Fcomes from.
OL,14,FWhile it is not mandatory, one
OL,15,Fpolitical movement believes that the
OL,16,Fnew rules will not apply to them.
