OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FValue Jersey was set up in October
OL,8,Fand, while not registered as a party,
OL,9,Fsays it plans to publish a manifesto
OL,10,Fand campaign on issues ahead of the
OL,11,FJune polls.
OL,13,FIt describes itself as a "community-
OL,14,Ffunded movement" that aims to examine
OL,15,Fideas and policies to make Jersey more
OL,16,Faffordable through teamwork and
OL,17,Fcollaboration.
