OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FSamantha Gleave, Director of
OL,8,FCommunications for Value Jersey,
OL,9,Fargues that since they are not
OL,10,Fendorsing candidates who stand, they
OL,11,Fdo not fall under the legislation.
OL,13,FShe added that while they are "all for
OL,14,Ftransparency", they were "bemused" by
OL,15,Fthe new law, dubbing it "bureaucracy
OL,16,Ffor the sake of bureaucracy".
