OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"I think the Jersey Electoral
OL,8,FAuthority made it very clear that the
OL,9,Fexisting laws do actually cover what
OL,10,FDeputy Rob Ward's proposition was
OL,11,Fultimately trying to do," Ms Gleave
OL,12,Ftold ITV News.
OL,14,F"It was quite flattering and was very
OL,15,Ftargeted towards us, and yet it
OL,16,Fexplicitly excluded us because it was
OL,17,Ffor movements that are endorsing
OL,18,Fcandidates, and we've made very clear
OL,19,Ffrom the beginning that we're not
OL,20,Fendorsing candidates.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
