OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"It's stifling the upcoming movements
OL,8,Fthat want to engage in debate and
OL,9,Fcreating more of a barrier to
OL,10,Fpolitical involvement."
OL,12,FITV News also asked whether Value
OL,13,FJersey would be sharing where they
OL,14,Freceive donations, which Ms Gleave
OL,15,Fsays the movement is "currently
OL,16,Freviewing".
