OL,7,F"We are absolutely up for transparency
OL,8,F(...) we've been relying on donations
OL,9,Ffrom local individuals, but we have to
OL,10,Frespect their privacy, and I'm not
OL,11,Feven sure with the current data laws,
OL,12,Fwhether we would retrospectively be
OL,13,Fable to even say who those individuals
OL,14,Fare.
