OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"The more you go down the route of
OL,8,Fforcing movements and collaborations,
OL,9,Fwhich they weren't actually able to
OL,10,Fdefine in the States what
OL,11,Fcollaborations were, you begin to
OL,12,Fstifle debate, and I think that's a
OL,13,Freally dangerous place to go."
OL,15,FThe largest political party in the
OL,16,Fisland is Reform Jersey, led by Deputy
OL,17,FSam Mezec, who believes political
OL,18,Fparties are a "more democratic and
OL,19,Fefficient way" to be involved in
OL,20,Fgovernment.
