OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,FHe told ITV News that Reform Jersey
OL,8,Fwas happy to follow the rules on
OL,9,Ffunding, and that the new rules "go
OL,10,Ffar enough" to incentivise political
OL,11,Fparties to declare themselves, even if
OL,12,Fit's not mandatory.
OL,14,F"It empowers voters to ask candidates
OL,15,Fwho choose not to abide by that code
OL,16,Fof practice," Deputy Mezec explained.
OL,18,F"What have you got to hide? Why won't
OL,19,Fyou sign up for it? Why won't you tell
OL,20,Fus where your funding is coming from?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
