OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F386A1769652988
OL,3,CNew rules passed on declaring
OL,4,Cpolitical groups as Jersey's election
OL,5,Clooms
OL,7,F"I've got nothing to hide. Our party's
OL,8,Fgot nothing to hide. Why would any
OL,9,Fother candidate not commit to doing
OL,10,Fthe same unless they've got something
OL,11,Fto hide?"
OL,13,FDeputy Mezec added that Value Jersey
OL,14,Fshould "absolutely" call itself a
OL,15,Fpolitical party.
OL,17,F"They should abide by the same rules
OL,18,Fas the rest of us. In our democracy,
OL,19,Fwe're meant to all be equal, and the
OL,20,Frules are meant to apply across the
OL,21,Fboard. No one is above that."
